      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six. This A80 chassis remains a benchmark of over-engineered performance, utilizing a sequential induction system that ensures minimal lag and a robust mid-range torque curve. Power is managed through the highly sought-after Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec helical limited-slip differential. The vehicle maintains its structural integrity with a tight double-wishbone suspension setup, offering precise damping and predictable turn-in. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina typical of a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals are excellent, with consistent compression across all cylinders and smooth gear synchronization. This is a high-performance icon ready for the open road, emphasizing drivetrain reliability and authentic analog feedback.",
